<i>T. m. fuscipennis</i> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tommaso_Salvadori" title="Tommaso Salvadori">Salvadori</a>, 1895)<sup id="cite_ref-BS_2-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BS-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></small><br />
<i>T. m. castaneiceps</i> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tommaso_Salvadori" title="Tommaso Salvadori">Salvadori</a>, 1895)<sup id="cite_ref-BS_2-4" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BS-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></small><br />
<i>T. m. brunniventris</i> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aldrich" title="Aldrich">Aldrich</a>, 1937)<sup id="cite_ref-BS_2-5" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BS-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></small><br />
<i>T. m. saturatus</i> <small>(<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ludlow_Griscom" title="Ludlow Griscom">Griscom</a>, 1929)<sup id="cite_ref-BS_2-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BS-2"><span>[</span>2<span>]</span></a></sup></small><br />
